OL,6,FBut it has been a slow burning success
OL,7,Fwith the daytime audience even though
OL,8,Fit has had little publicity. It often
OL,9,Fgets significantly more viewers than
OL,10,FLorraine and This Morning on ITV 1
OL,11,Fthough you would never know it from
OL,12,Fthe tabloids and celebrity mags.
OL,14,FMost of the content can hardly be
OL,15,Fcalled innovative but it has a genuine
OL,16,Fwarmth and sincerity while
OL,17,Foccasionally the content takes an
OL,18,Funexpected turn.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/7
