OL,3,CMore difficult decisions ahead for the
OL,4,CBBC
OL,6,FIt's a quality daytime magazine,
OL,7,Fquietly created, in the best
OL,8,Ftraditions of Pebble Mill at One,
OL,9,FAfternoon Plus and, yes, This Morning
OL,10,Fbefore it became celebrity obsessed.
OL,12,FToday came the welcome news it will be
OL,13,Fextended by half an hour in January.
OL,15,FTogether with the extension of
OL,16,FBreakfast to 9.30am, it will give BBC
OL,17,FOne's morning schedule a greater focus
OL,18,Fon live output.
